Detailed Description

cvmx_srio::_rx_bell_seq

This register contains the value of the sequence counter when the doorbell was received and a shadow copy of the bell FIFO count that can be read without emptying the FIFO. This register must be read prior to SRIO()_RX_BELL to guarantee that the information corresponds to the correct doorbell.

This register is reset by the h-clock reset.
